=== FASTag 1033 Helpline Call Script ===

Dial: 1033 (NHAI / IHMCL national FASTag helpline, 24x7).

Keep these ready BEFORE you call:
  • Vehicle number: {VEHICLE_NO}
  • FASTag ID (Tag serial, ~17 chars from the tag sticker): {TAG_ID}
  • Transaction ID / Plaza ID: {TXN_ID}
  • Date & time of deduction: {TXN_DATETIME}
  • Toll plaza name / highway: {PLAZA_NAME}
  • Lane ID (if visible): {LANE_ID}
  • Amount deducted: Rs. {AMOUNT}
  • Nature of dispute: {ISSUE_TYPE}

Open the conversation with:
  "Namaskar, I want to report a false FASTag deduction. My vehicle number is {VEHICLE_NO}, FASTag ID {TAG_ID}, at {PLAZA_NAME} on {TXN_DATETIME} for Rs. {AMOUNT}. The deduction was incorrect because {ISSUE_TYPE}. Please register my complaint and issue a complaint reference number."

Insist on:
  1. A verbal complaint reference (ask the agent to repeat it).
  2. SMS / WhatsApp confirmation with the complaint ID.
  3. Expected resolution date (typically 7 working days).
  4. Ask for IHMCL false-deduction case ID if applicable.

After the call: open the Refund Radar dispute record and paste the complaint ID into the ticket-no field, and tick "Mark as filed" to start the 30-day window.

If 1033 doesn't resolve in 7 days, escalate to:
  - falsededuction@ihmcl.com (email with this template's data), AND
  - This app's Ombudsman template against NHAI if unresolved for 30 days.

